c t pmc
c Projected variables: {1}
c Non-projection Comp A: {2,3} — always SAT (clause 2v3), disconnected from var 1
c Non-projection Comp C1: {4,5,6} — UNSAT when 1=T
c   (4v5),(4v-5) => 4=T; (-4v6),(-4v-6) => 6=T and 6=F => contradiction
c Non-projection Comp C2: {7,8} — SAT when 1=T (clause 7v8)
c
c When 1=T: internalSAT(C2={7,8})=SAT contributes 1, then internalSAT(C1={4,5,6})=UNSAT
c   Bug: without markBranchUnsat(), accumulated 1 from C2 wrongly propagates -> answer 2
c   Fix: markBranchUnsat() discards C2's contribution -> answer 1
c When 1=F: all -1 clauses satisfied, no constraint on 4-8 -> 1 projected model
c
c Expected PMC answer: 1
p cnf 8 6
c p show 1 0
2 3 0
-1 4 5 0
-1 4 -5 0
-1 -4 6 0
-1 -4 -6 0
-1 7 8 0
